OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police will review
OL,7,Fwhether pro-Palestine marches can go
OL,8,Fahead in the wake of the Golders Green
OL,9,Fattack as the head of the force
OL,10,Fclashed with Green Party leader Zack
OL,11,FPolanski.
OL,13,FThe Met said police will be assessing
OL,14,Fevents across the country after the UK
OL,15,Fterrorism threat level was raised to
OL,16,F"severe" after the stabbings.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
