OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777593773
OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer ` who
OL,7,Fis facing calls to ban pro-Palestine
OL,8,Fmarches ` backed the prosecution of
OL,9,Fpeople at such events chanting
OL,10,F"globalise the intifada".
OL,12,FThe Stop the War Coalition is planning
OL,13,Fa major demonstration in London on May
OL,14,F16 to mark Nakba Day, commemorating
OL,15,Fthe 1948 displacement of Palestinians
OL,16,Fduring the creation of Israel.
OL,18,FThe group has described attempts to
OL,19,Flink recent attacks with marches as
OL,20,F"false".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]|D@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
