OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FAsked about upcoming marches, head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing Assistant
OL,8,FCommissioner Laurence Taylor said: "As
OL,9,Fpart of our review into the change in
OL,10,Fthe threat level, policing will be
OL,11,Freviewing all events across the
OL,12,Fcountry."
OL,14,FIn a rare intervention on Thursday,
OL,15,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley
OL,16,Fcriticised Mr Polanski for retweeting
OL,17,Fan X post accusing officers of
OL,18,F"repeatedly and violently kicking a
OL,19,Fmentally ill man in the head" when he
OL,20,Fwas already incapacitated from being
OL,21,Ftasered.
OL,26,@pD@dOUtD@IO]zD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
