OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777593773
OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FSir Mark Rowley said he was
OL,7,F"disappointed", adding that the post
OL,8,Fwas "inaccurate and misinformed".
OL,10,F"Your decision to criticise these
OL,11,Fofficers, using your public profile
OL,12,Fand reach will have a chilling
OL,13,Feffect," he added.
OL,15,FA Green Party spokesperson said Mr
OL,16,FPolanski "knows it was a very
OL,17,Fdifficult situation for the
OL,18,Fauthorities".
