OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FScotland Yard has declined to comment
OL,7,Fon a Channel 4 News report that the
OL,8,Fsuspect ` named earlier as Essa
OL,9,FSuleiman ` left a psychiatric hospital
OL,10,Frun by South London and Maudsley NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust in recent days.
OL,13,FHe was born in Somalia and came to the
OL,14,FUK legally as a child in the 1990s,
OL,15,Fand was reported to Prevent, the
OL,16,FGovernment's anti-extremism programme,
OL,17,Fin 2020 but the case was closed the
OL,18,Fsame year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
