OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FPolice tasered and arrested a 45-year-
OL,7,Fold man after the double stabbing
OL,8,Fwhich saw two Jewish men ` Shloime
OL,9,FRand, 34, and Moshe Ben Baila, 76,
OL,10,Fnamed locally as Moshe Shine ` taken
OL,11,Fto hospital.
OL,13,FMr Rand told the BBC it was a
OL,14,F"miracle" he survived, adding: "I feel
OL,15,Flike God's given me back my life."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@IO]vD@`OUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
