CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777593773
OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FHe has since been discharged from
OL,7,Fhospital and is now recovering at home
OL,8,Fafter receiving stitches, Rabbi Levi
OL,9,FSchapiro, from the Jewish Community
OL,10,FCouncil and who has visited both
OL,11,Fvictims, said on social media.
OL,13,FMr Shine remains in hospital and in a
OL,14,Fstable condition.
OL,16,FThe Joint Terrorism Analysis Centre
OL,17,Fraised the threat level to "severe" on
OL,18,FThursday, meaning a terror attack is
OL,19,F"highly likely".
OL,26,@yD@\OUyD@cO]{D@AOU{D@OO]
