OL,3,CMet considers ban on pro-Palestine
OL,4,Cmarches as Rowley and Polanski clash
OL,6,FThe decision is not solely a result of
OL,7,Fthe Golders Green attack, the Home
OL,8,FOffice said, adding that the threat
OL,9,Flevel in the UK has been "rising for
OL,10,Fsome time".
